Usage: setWhatIfTimingMode [-help] [-reset] [-context {in|out}]
                           [-defaultOutputCap <number>]
                           [-model {intrinsic|normalized}]
                           [-portPriority {cellType|portParam}]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-reset                                 # Resets all or specified options to default value
-context {in|out}                      # Mode Description
                                       # (enums={in out}, default=out)
-defaultOutputCap <number>             # Default Output Capacitance
                                       # (float, default=0)
-model {intrinsic|normalized}          # Model
                                       # (enums={intrinsic normalized}, default=normalized)
-portPriority {cellType|portParam}     # Port Priority
                                       # (enums={cellType portParam}, default=portParam)